@node "usage" "Usage"

@{b}@{u}Starting EZMake@{ub}@{uu}

EZMake can be started from
  shell/cli
  Workbench(no tooltypes yet)

TEMPLATE: FILE/K,QUIT/S,C=COMPILE/S,TOP/N,LEFT/N
  FILE		a ezmke file
  QUIT		quits ezmake(after compiling)
  COMPILE	emulates the MAKE button after loading the ezmke file
  TOP/LEFT	window opening position

EXAMPLE: EZMake file=ezmake.ezmke quit compile


